Deep Mem0 modifies and extends Mem0 with, among other changes:
  - First-class multilingual retrieval (Portuguese in addition to English):
    language-aware BM25 sparse encoding, language-aware lemmatization with
    fail-safe fallbacks, multilingual default embedder and reranker, and
    reranker over-fetch.
  - Human-memory dynamics: frequency (reinforcement) and recency (forgetting
    curve) weighting of retrieval, based on ACT-R base-level activation.

